data.description: This charming 1772 sqft home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with an inviting open floor plan that creates a spacious and welcoming atmosphere. The interior has been tastefully updated, featuring granite counters in the kitchen and bathrooms, that add a touch of elegance. The kitchen boasts a gas stove for culinary convenience, while an inside laundry area adds practicality. Outside, a spacious backyard awaits your creativity. With a tile roof, newer HVAC, and water heater, this home is move-in ready, offering comfort and efficiency. Located near shopping, Merced College, UC Merced, and medical facilities. Embrace the opportunity to start anew in this remarkable property!
